        CHANGES IN spatstat.local VERSION 4.1-0

OVERVIEW

    o Minor updates to version dependence.

        CHANGES IN spatstat.local VERSION 4.0-0

OVERVIEW

    o spatstat.local now depends on 'spatstat.geom' and 'spatstat.core'
    rather than 'spatstat'.
    
    o added NEWS file.

SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o package dependence
    The 'spatstat' package has been divided into a series of sub-packages.
    This extension package 'spatstat.local' now depends on the
    sub-packages 'spatstat.geom', 'spatstat.core', 'spatstat.sparse'
    and 'spatstat.data'.
    
    o NEWS
    This NEWS file has been added to the package at version 4.0-0.

